  "text": "Cardiovascular diseases [CITATION_1] and stroke [CITATION_2] have been associated with a higher DDDI risk. However, we found no association between cardiovascular diseases or stroke and DDDIs in our sample, although a trend (p ¼ 0.07) emerged between coronary heart disease and DDDIs. This may have clinical implications since cardiovascular diseases are so common in frail populations.",
